goal.en:
Upon successful completion of this course, students will be able to: 
1. develop a better understanding of intercultural communication and explore symbolic connection between culture and communication; 
2. learn more about the complexity of cultural identities;
3. learn more about both verbal and non-verbal communication; 
4. communicate better in different cultural contexts; 
5. improve critical thinking in terms of the 4 skills in English, and
6. cultivate intercultural communication competence.
